Since the early 70's{Newborough}has had a{Well Dressing}each year in{May} with{Maypole Dancing}and a{Fete.}
Other events during the year include a{Flower Festival}in the Church, a Women's Institute{Produce Show,}an { {'Over Sixties' Fayre}organised by the Happy Circle and a{Church Fete.}
The Church in addition has a{Harvest {Festival}and organises several money raising functions such as{dances, {cheese and wine, whist drives}and{ {coffee evenings.}A{Church Magazine}is also produced with a circulation of around 70.
There is{handbell ringing,}a famous hunt nearby - the{Meynell,}and{cricket on the local ground.
